Class Branch

java.lang.Object
Branch
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Branch extends Object implements Serializable
The Branch class represents a branch of a restaurant or business. It contains information about the users, menu, and orders associated with the branch. This class implements the Serializable interface to allow for object serialization.
